lead_paragraph: Honda's Marc Marquez took pole position for his home Catalunya MotoGP race on Saturday on an all-Spanish front row a day after compatriot Luis Salom's fatal accident in Moto2 practice.

headline.print_headline: Marquez on Pole for Catalunya MotoGP
